Date: Wed, 24 Sep 2025 12:02:44 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] net: ethernet: mtk_eth_soc: change to internal ppe debugfs

Without this patch, users cannot get the Bind or Unbind entries
with a single debug command.

Signed-off-by: Bo-Cun Chen <bc-bocun.chen@mediatek.com>
---
 drivers/net/ethernet/mediatek/mtk_eth_soc.c   |  4 ++++
 1 files changed, 4 insertions(+)

--- a/drivers/net/ethernet/mediatek/mtk_eth_soc.c
+++ b/drivers/net/ethernet/mediatek/mtk_eth_soc.c
@@ -7117,6 +7117,10 @@ static int mtk_probe(struct platform_dev
 			if (err)
 				goto err_deinit_ppe;
 		}
+
+		err = mtk_ppe_internal_debugfs_init(eth);
+		if (err)
+			goto err_deinit_ppe;
 	}
 
